name: Jiva Juice
address: Jl. Raya Sempidi No.123, Lukluk, Kec. Mengwi, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80351, Indonesia
types: vegan_restaurant, vegetarian_restaurant, health, restaurant, food, store
review 1: Been living in Bali living the typical healthy Bali life, sunsets with drinks, night outs with drinks, I realized I felt unenergized, and my friend said I should try juicing. They had just finished a Jiva Juice cleanse and highly recommended Jiva after having a wonderful experience herself. So I've just finished a 7 days juice detox I did a super cleanse which was 4lts per day of all different juices which helped keep it interesting, plus I received a free bottle of Jiva detox water. To be honest the first couple days I felt pretty bad, but I pushed on, and by the end of the juicing I felt very uplifted energized probably the best I've felt in a long time. Overall I'm very thankful to Jiva and now starting to just order juices on a regular basis because I feel something is missing now when I don't have juice in the fridge.
review 2: My friends and I have been ordering this juice for months now and this is one of the best cold pressed juices Bali has to offer. Great delivery as well and good prices. Highly recommend for fasting on as well and/or daily nutrition in general while eating. Bottle has a nice design with list of ingredients and benefits.
review 3: The first time I was given Jiva's juice by a friend of mine, I was blown away. Now whenever I'm in Bali, I order Jiva everyday for the rest of my trip. I wish they are also in Jakarta!! But recently got myself a juicer, after drinking Jiva it not only introduce me to a very good tasting juice but also changed my lifestyle completely. Now not a day I go by without getting my juice intake. All thanks to Jiva Creations.
review 4: Absolutely amazing juices. Best quality with only the best organic ingredients. No preservatives. They have a broad range to choose from. And great delivery service. Two thumbs up for excellent quality and service!
review 5: The best cold pressed juice in Bali. Makes my life easier with free delivery and great service
